'''Russia''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, Moscow, along with St. Petersburg.

Although Russia is currently in a state of war due to the invasion of Ukraine, there are no [[Death|deaths]] related to terrorist or battlefield attacks.
